  * Merge from debian, remaining changes:
    - don't build against libdirac, lame, libopenjpeg, librtmp, 
      x264, and xvid  (all in universe)

 -- Reinhard Tartler <siretart@tauware.de>  Sat, 21 Jan 2012 09:34:37 +0100

